00:42:54,240 --> 00:43:00,020
Arabic grammar possesses specific structural constructions that explicitly formalize this divide.

724
00:43:00,020 --> 00:43:06,300
It contains possessive frameworks that literally tether subjective opinions like beauty directly to the observer,

