00:43:21,900 --> 00:43:26,460
When attempting to describe the immutable core of the object, the noun at the center of the hierarchy,

730
00:43:26,940 --> 00:43:28,860
the Arabic term deployed was jawar.

731
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:29,480
Jawar.

