00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,380
It is exactly that.

761
00:45:26,480 --> 00:45:32,040
The English adjective sequence is an unconscious mathematical formalization of the exact metaphysical distinction

762
00:45:32,040 --> 00:45:34,940
that Aristotle, Al-Farabi, and Ibn Sina theorized.

763
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:36,020
That's just wild.

764
00:45:36,020 --> 00:45:39,220
Every single time a human being fluently utters the phrase,

765
00:45:39,600 --> 00:45:45,300
a small red wooden box, their brain is rigorously executing Aristotelian substance theory.

766
00:45:46,020 --> 00:45:53,420
We are effortlessly sorting the physical universe into essential jawar and temporary karin at conversational speed

767
00:45:53,420 --> 00:45:56,700
without ever realizing the philosophical depth of the computation.

768
00:45:57,040 --> 00:45:59,560
It fundamentally changes how you view language.

769
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:03,760
We aren't just communicating, we are philosophizing at blinding speeds.

770
00:46:03,760 --> 00:46:07,680
And if this sorting algorithm is truly rooted in universal physics,

771
00:46:08,020 --> 00:46:10,520
cognitive processing limits, and ancient metaphysics,

