775
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:22,040
The paper closes by establishing this as a universal framework,

776
00:46:22,440 --> 00:46:24,600
making definitive cross-linguistic predictions.

777
00:46:25,260 --> 00:46:28,900
It states that if navigational pressure is the true engine of lexical preservation,

778
00:46:29,300 --> 00:46:31,040
we will find its fingerprints everywhere.

779
00:46:31,180 --> 00:46:31,520
Everywhere.

