797
00:47:45,620 --> 00:47:50,580
English spatial sequences, Spanish verb toggles, and Mandarin nominal classifiers.

798
00:47:50,960 --> 00:47:56,820
They're all just different technological solutions engineered by human cultures to solve the exact same physics problem.

799
00:47:57,180 --> 00:48:03,400
